'''Andrin Foods''' was a [[Foodstuff/Legends|foodstuff]] manufacturing company that smuggled weapons for the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]].

{{Company-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
Containers of this company can be seen in mission 5:3. If the player inspects them before proceeding to the main objectives, one can see their true cargo, hidden blasters, and hidden weapons. They don't have a role in the mission objectives.

